  <summary date="2021-03-31T19:45:13Z" status="Introduced in House">Apprenticeships to College Act

This bill requires the Department of Labor to enter into an interagency agreement with the Department of Education to promote and support integration and alignment of programs under the national apprenticeship system with secondary, 2- and 4-year postsecondary, and adult education.</summary>
